#Steps to install NagiosCore on a Centos7 server

Steps followed are from the Nagios Website here:

$ https://support.nagios.com/kb/article/nagios-core-installing-nagios-core-from-source.html#CentOS

This link provides all the steps you need to install the Nagios Core system.

